Body: What We've Learned Updated: Customer is getting Proxy initialization error on FSAC jobs. It was determined during the call that they didn't setup the correct proxy server in the job settings and specified a server that didn't had the FSAA Proxy executable installed. Setting that to correct server resulted in successful execution of the job. However, the customer now wants to setup a different proxy and they are getting same errors.
Next Steps Updated: The customer has been asked to verify the permissions and ports for proxy servers as per documentation.
